Relationship to Orange Home

Orange Home	Sine Square

learns from input	learns from output
interprets player	reshapes interpreter
condenses rules	reshapes rule condensation
starting point	recursive modifier


Together, they form a loop:

> player → host → cartridge → host → player



This loop is central to Home.


